# GEMINI_API_KEY: enables the AI Assistant component's real Gemini-backed
# responses. Optional — if unset, the /api/gemini/assistant route falls back
# to keyword-matched canned responses instead of failing. Note: the AI
# Assistant is not currently linked from any page, so this key has no
# effect on the rest of the app either way. See docs/API.md.
GEMINI_API_KEY=
